TRACKER: He is that.

01:00:27.850 --> 01:00:30.650
There's a tenderness
l never knew in life.

01:00:31.050 --> 01:00:33.550
l didn't know him
when he was young.

01:00:35.290 --> 01:00:37.590
Were you proud
of your own kids?

01:00:39.600 --> 01:00:40.930
Of course.

01:00:41.430 --> 01:00:44.260
That's an easy
bullshit answer.

01:00:45.900 --> 01:00:47.430
Think about it.

01:00:49.370 --> 01:00:51.100
l said "Of course."

01:00:52.880 --> 01:00:54.780
l like this sore point.

01:00:55.080 --> 01:00:57.840
lts juice... Juice is strong.
lt connects.

01:00:59.150 --> 01:01:01.740
Makes you a better receiver
for Annie.

01:01:04.990 --> 01:01:08.220
She's the transmitter,
sending thoughts of you.

01:01:11.560 --> 01:01:12.820
(GASPING)

