01:01:37.090 --> 01:01:39.720
We can be reborn.

01:01:39.820 --> 01:01:41.810
But only if we choose to.

01:01:43.330 --> 01:01:45.590
Last trip,
l did the same work...

01:01:45.660 --> 01:01:47.320
You were a shrink!

01:01:48.400 --> 01:01:50.060
Fairly perceptive.

01:01:56.240 --> 01:01:57.600
Oh, my God.

