01:11:09.160 --> 01:11:10.350
l'll concentrate harder!

01:11:10.430 --> 01:11:13.330
You don't know how.
You're all mouth and no chops!

01:11:13.400 --> 01:11:15.920
All you're good for
is she loves you.

01:11:16.200 --> 01:11:18.570
Your boy is
a decisive distraction.

01:11:18.630 --> 01:11:19.690
Damn shrinks!

01:11:19.770 --> 01:11:21.170
You love
shoving people around!

01:11:21.240 --> 01:11:23.710
We're going down
to the bottom.
His last chance.

01:11:23.770 --> 01:11:25.670
He's never been
in such a place.

01:11:25.740 --> 01:11:29.800
You haven't. lt's better
watching one than two.

01:11:30.410 --> 01:11:31.540
You want him clear?

01:11:31.610 --> 01:11:34.080
Screw him, lan.
He doesn't know us.

01:11:34.150 --> 01:11:35.740
He's not family!

01:11:36.450 --> 01:11:38.420
No! l'm not leaving him.

01:11:43.090 --> 01:11:44.890
lf he never sees her?

01:11:45.190 --> 01:11:46.920
Never says goodbye?

01:11:48.860 --> 01:11:51.300
We do it without him.
We do it together.
She's your mother.

01:11:51.370 --> 01:11:52.390
Let's go!

01:11:52.470 --> 01:11:54.330
Dad, no. Listen to me.

01:11:58.310 --> 01:12:01.000
When you get there,
don't listen to him.

01:12:03.050 --> 01:12:04.450
You find her

01:12:05.720 --> 01:12:07.620
and you bring her back.

01:12:08.650 --> 01:12:10.140
You can do it.

01:12:12.020 --> 01:12:13.650
l believe in you.

01:12:25.170 --> 01:12:27.970
Do you ever think
why l chose to be Albert?

01:12:28.440 --> 01:12:31.240
He was the only guy
you ever listened to.

01:12:31.440 --> 01:12:33.070
Listen to me now!

01:12:33.640 --> 01:12:35.240
Think about Mom!

01:12:36.210 --> 01:12:38.840
Think about what happened
when we died!

01:12:39.580 --> 01:12:42.850
