to her to bring her back!

01:13:16.020 --> 01:13:17.750
(MUFFLED SCREAMING)

01:13:29.100 --> 01:13:31.070
ALBERT: Think about Mom.

01:13:35.200 --> 01:13:37.200
Think about when we died.

01:13:44.750 --> 01:13:47.240
ANNIE:
l'm teaching myself to smoke.

01:13:49.420 --> 01:13:52.250
The doctors call it
an affirmation of life.

01:13:57.230 --> 01:13:59.520
Well, it beats
the statue thing.

01:14:03.800 --> 01:14:05.530
You said "divorce".

01:14:06.340 --> 01:14:08.130
You got my attention.

01:14:11.570 --> 01:14:13.870
l think that
we're too different

01:14:15.480 --> 01:14:17.110
to stay together.

01:14:19.780 --> 01:14:21.050
l mean...

01:14:23.350 --> 01:14:26.250
Well, for one thing,
why aren't you in here?

01:14:28.590 --> 01:14:30.560
Why didn't you go crazy?

01:14:32.900 --> 01:14:34.620
Your children died.

01:14:35.460 --> 01:14:36.830
l remember.

01:14:38.700 --> 01:14:41.190
l remember the silence
in the house.

01:14:42.200 --> 01:14:44.800
l thought l was supposed
to be strong.

01:14:48.540 --> 01:14:50.030
For me?
For me.

01:14:50.850 --> 01:14:51.840
For us.

01:14:51.910 --> 01:14:54.010
Just on general principles.

01:14:55.680 --> 01:14:57.450
l loved them, Annie.

01:14:58.920 --> 01:15:00.550
But they're gone.

01:15:04.360 --> 01:15:06.120
You've got a choice.

01:15:06.330 --> 01:15:08.060
Life either goes on

01:15:10.530 --> 01:15:11.730
or not.

01:15:12.700 --> 01:15:14.470
And you choose life.

01:15:19.310 --> 01:15:22.110
Sometimes,
when you win, you lose.

